Terrosaur:




Terrorsaur stepped out of the pod. He looked around, eyeing Dark Mouse, 
Scorponok, Megatron and Waspinator quickly. His dull red eyes looked at 
every corner of the cave in curiosity.

He heard Waspintor speak, calling him a bird, when he knew even was a 
dactyl. "Remember you?" he said. He shook his head. "I've never seen you 
before." Why would this bot say he would know him? He had just been brought 
on-line.

He looked over to Megatron.
